{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"0434d367-c6b7-482c-8ca7-37c5165ef1eb","agentId":"a8dc0cc368bd89e4e","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are implementing Task 9: CLI Entry Point and Environment Config\n\n## Task Description\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `bin/import.php`\n- Create: `.env.example`\n\n### .env.example content:\n\n```\n# .env.example\nAPI_BASE_URL=https://pds.xsalto.com\nAPI_LOGIN=AVORIAZ\nAPI_PASSWORD=Avoriaz@2026\nDB_HOST=localhost\nDB_PORT=5432\nDB_NAME=xsalto_fidelity\nDB_USER=postgres\nDB_PASSWORD=\nPAGE_SIZE=100\n```\n\n### bin/import.php content:\n\n```php\n<?php\n// bin/import.php\nrequire __DIR__ . '/../vendor/autoload.php';\n\n// Minimal .env loader (no extra dependencies)\nif (file_exists(__DIR__ . '/../.env')) {\n    foreach (file(__DIR__ . '/../.env', FILE_IGNORE_NEW_LINES | FILE_SKIP_EMPTY_LINES) as $line) {\n        if (str_starts_with(trim($line), '#') || !str_contains($line, '=')) {\n            continue;\n        }\n        [$key, $value] = explode('=', $line, 2);\n        $_ENV[trim($key)] = trim($value);\n    }\n}\n\nuse Xav\\XsaltoPdsFid\\ApiClient\\XsaltoApiClient;\nuse Xav\\XsaltoPdsFid\\Config\\DatabaseConfig;\nuse Xav\\XsaltoPdsFid\\Database\\ContactRepository;\nuse Xav\\XsaltoPdsFid\\Database\\PageTracker;\nuse Xav\\XsaltoPdsFid\\Importer\\ContactImporter;\nuse Xav\\XsaltoPdsFid\\Mapper\\ContactMapper;\n\n$apiClient = new XsaltoApiClient($_ENV['API_BASE_URL'] ?? 'https://pds.xsalto.com');\n$apiClient->login($_ENV['API_LOGIN'], $_ENV['API_PASSWORD']);\n\n$connection = DatabaseConfig::createConnection();\n\n$importer = new ContactImporter(\n    $apiClient,\n    new ContactRepository($connection),\n    new PageTracker($connection),\n    new ContactMapper(),\n    (int) ($_ENV['PAGE_SIZE'] ?? 100),\n);\n\n$importer->import();\n```\n\n### Commit:\n```bash\ngit add bin/import.php .env.example\ngit commit -m \"feat: add CLI entry point and env configuration template\"\n```\n\n## Context\n\nWorking directory: `/home/xav/Workspace/ElibertyRepos/xsalto-pds-fid`\n\nAll PHP classes are already implemented:\n- `src/ApiClient/XsaltoApiClient.php`\n- `src/Config/DatabaseConfig.php`\n- `src/Database/ContactRepository.php`\n- `src/Database/PageTracker.php`\n- `src/Importer/ContactImporter.php`\n- `src/Mapper/ContactMapper.php`\n\nThe CLI entry point wires them all together. It uses a minimal `.env` loader that parses `KEY=VALUE` lines (skips comments starting with `#` and lines without `=`). The `.env` file is optional — if not present, defaults are used. The `.env.example` serves as a template.\n\nImportant: Do NOT create a `.env` file (only `.env.example`). The actual `.env` with real credentials is created by the user from the example.\n\nAlso create a `.gitignore` to exclude `.env` and `vendor/`:\n\n```\nvendor/\n.env\n```\n\nCommit .gitignore along with the other files.\n\n## Your Job\n\n1. Create `bin/` directory\n2. Write `bin/import.php`\n3. Write `.env.example`\n4. Write `.gitignore`\n5. Run `vendor/bin/phpunit` to confirm all tests still pass\n6. Commit\n7. Report back\n\n## Report Format\n\n- **Status:** DONE | BLOCKED\n- Files changed\n- Test results\n"},"uuid":"0de61f00-8bcd-47f6-ab48-953cfa389fad","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:26:52.426Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/home/xav/Workspace/ElibertyRepos/xsalto-pds-fid","sessionId":"7adf6774-7b0d-45b6-aa96-f0c904ea4708","version":"2.1.85","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"compiled-riding-pinwheel"}
